<!DOCTYPE html>

<html lang="en">

<head>

<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Mentor Management | TESRECO</title>

<style>

*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Segoe UI',sans-serif;
}

body{
    min-height:100vh;
    background:linear-gradient(
    135deg,
    #1e3a8a,
    #2563eb,
    #60a5fa);
}

.navbar{
    width:100%;
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    backdrop-filter:blur(12px);
    padding:18px 50px;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
}

.logo{
    color:white;
    font-size:28px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

.nav-links a{
    text-decoration:none;
    color:white;
    margin-left:25px;
    font-weight:600;
}

.nav-links a:hover{
    color:#ffd700;
}

.container{
    width:90%;
    max-width:1200px;
    margin:40px auto;
}

.header{
    text-align:center;
    color:white;
    margin-bottom:40px;
}

.header h1{
    font-size:48px;
    margin-bottom:10px;
}

.header p{
    font-size:18px;
}

.grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;
    gap:30px;
}

.card{
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
    backdrop-filter:blur(15px);
    border-radius:20px;
    padding:35px;
    box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
}

.card h2{
    color:white;
    margin-bottom:25px;
}

.form-group{
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

.form-group label{
    display:block;
    color:white;
    margin-bottom:8px;
    font-weight:600;
}

.form-group input{
    width:100%;
    padding:14px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:10px;
    outline:none;
    font-size:15px;
}

.btn{
    width:100%;
    padding:15px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:10px;
    background:#ffd700;
    color:#1e3a8a;
    font-size:17px;
    font-weight:bold;
    cursor:pointer;
    transition:0.3s;
}

.btn:hover{
    transform:translateY(-3px);
}

.info-box{
    background:white;
    padding:20px;
    border-radius:12px;
    margin-bottom:15px;
    transition:0.3s;
}

.info-box:hover{
    transform:translateY(-4px);
}

.info-box h3{
    color:#1e3a8a;
    margin-bottom:8px;
}

.info-box p{
    color:#555;
}

.stats{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);
    gap:15px;
    margin-top:30px;
}

.stat{
    background:white;
    border-radius:12px;
    padding:20px;
    text-align:center;
}

.stat h2{
    color:#2563eb;
}

.stat p{
    color:#555;
}

@media(max-width:900px){

.grid{
    grid-template-columns:1fr;
}

.header h1{
    font-size:36px;
}

}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="navbar">

```
<div class="logo">
    TESRECO
</div>

<div class="nav-links">

    <a href="/home">Home</a>
   
    <a href="/add">Add Intern</a>
    <a href="/view">View Interns</a>
    <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>

</div>
```

</div>

<div class="container">

```
<div class="header">

    <h1>Mentor Management Portal</h1>

    <p>
        Add mentors, manage expertise and assign guidance
        to internship programs.
    </p>

</div>

<div class="grid">

    <div class="card">

        <h2>Add New Mentor</h2>

        <form action="/add_mentor" method="POST">

            <div class="form-group">

                <label>Mentor Name</label>

                <input
                type="text"
                name="name"
                placeholder="Enter Mentor Name"
                required>

            </div>

            <div class="form-group">

                <label>Specialization</label>

                <input
                type="text"
                name="specialization"
                placeholder="Data Science, AI, Web Development..."
                required>

            </div>

            <button class="btn">
                Add Mentor
            </button>

        </form>

    </div>

    <div class="card">

        <h2>Mentorship Benefits</h2>

        <div class="info-box">

            <h3>Career Guidance</h3>

            <p>
                Help interns understand industry expectations
                and career opportunities.
            </p>

        </div>

        <div class="info-box">

            <h3>Project Support</h3>

            <p>
                Guide interns in completing real-world
                projects successfully.
            </p>

        </div>

        <div class="info-box">

            <h3>Skill Development</h3>

            <p>
                Improve technical and professional skills.
            </p>

        </div>

    </div>

</div>

<div class="stats">

    <div class="stat">

        <h2>15+</h2>

        <p>Mentors</p>

    </div>

    <div class="stat">

        <h2>8+</h2>

        <p>Domains</p>

    </div>

    <div class="stat">

        <h2>100+</h2>

        <p>Interns Guided</p>

    </div>

</div>
```

</div>

</body>

</html>
